    • 字段详细资料

      • backgrounds_enabled

        public boolean backgrounds_enabled
        Set to true to print background graphics or false to not print background graphics.
        设置为true可打印背景图形，设置为false则不打印背景图形。

      • header_footer_enabled

        public boolean header_footer_enabled
        Set to true to print headers and footers or false to not print headers and footers.
        设置为true以打印页眉和页脚，设置为false则不打印页眉和页脚。

      • header_footer_title

        public java.lang.String header_footer_title
        Page title to display in the header. Only used if header_footer_enabled is set to true.
        页面标题显示在标题中。仅在header_footer_enabled设置为true时使用。

      • header_footer_url

        public java.lang.String header_footer_url
        URL to display in the footer. Only used if header_footer_enabled is set to true.
        在页脚中显示的URL。仅在header_footer_enabled设置为true时使用。

      • landscape

        public boolean landscape
        Set to true for landscape mode or false for portrait mode.
        设置为true（横向）或false（纵向）。

      • margin_bottom

        public double margin_bottom

      • margin_left

        public double margin_left

      • margin_right

        public double margin_right

      • margin_top

        public double margin_top
        Margins in millimeters. Only used if |margin_type| is set to PDF_PRINT_MARGIN_CUSTOM.
        以毫米为单位的边距。仅在| margin_type |下使用设置为PDF_PRINT_MARGIN_CUSTOM。

      • margin_type

        public CefPdfPrintSettings.MarginType margin_type
        Margin type.
        保证金类型。

      • page_height

        public int page_height

      • page_width

        public int page_width
        Output page size in microns (1 millimeter = 1000 microns). If either of these values is less than or equal to zero then the default paper size will be used as returned by the print_handler. A4 is 210 297 mm which would be 210000 x 297000 microns. US Letter is 215.9 279.4 mm which would be 215900 x 279400 microns.
        输出页面大小，以微米为单位（1毫米= 1000微米）。如果这些值之一小于或等于零，则将使用由print_handler返回的默认纸张尺寸。 A4为210297毫米，即210000 x 297000微米。 US Letter为215.9279.4毫米，即215900 x 279400微米。

      • scale_factor

        public int scale_factor
        The percentage to scale the PDF by before printing (e.g. 50 is 50%). If this value is less than or equal to zero the default value of 100 will be used.
        打印前缩放PDF的百分比（例如50为50％）。如果此值小于或等于零，那么将使用默认值100。

      • selection_only

        public boolean selection_only
        Set to true to print the selection only or false to print all.
        设置为true仅打印选择内容，设置为false则打印全部内容。
